{
  "page": "The Sea Snake",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">This article is about the planned television series. For its main character, see <a href=\"/index.php/Corlys_Velaryon\" title=\"Corlys Velaryon\">Corlys Velaryon</a>. For the ship, see <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_Snake\" title=\"Sea Snake\">Sea Snake</a>.</div>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\"Nine Voyages\" and \"9 Voyages\" redirect here. For the text by Maester Mathis, see <a href=\"/index.php/The_Nine_Voyages\" title=\"The Nine Voyages\">The Nine Voyages</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox vevent\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"summary navbox-title\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-style: italic; background-color:&#91;&#91;:Template:Infobox television/colour&#93;&#93;;\">The Sea Snake</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre</th><td class=\"category\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fantasy\">Fantasy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Format</th><td class=\"category\">\nAnimated</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Created by</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruno_Heller\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Bruno Heller\">Bruno Heller</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Developed by</th><td>\nBruno Heller</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Written by</th><td>\nBruno Heller</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country of origin</th><td>\nUnited States</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language(s)</th><td>\nEnglish</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:&#91;&#91;:Template:Infobox television/colour&#93;&#93;;\">Production</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Executive <span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">producer(s)</span></th><td>\nBruno Heller</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Production <span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">company(s)</span></th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HBO\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:HBO\">HBO</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:&#91;&#91;:Template:Infobox television/colour&#93;&#93;;\">Chronology</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Related shows</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>The Sea Snake</b></i> (formerly <i><b>Nine Voyages</b></i>) is the working title of a planned American <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fantasy\">fantasy</a> television series, serving as a spin-off to the upcoming <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i> to explore the past of seafarer <a href=\"/index.php/Corlys_Velaryon\" title=\"Corlys Velaryon\">Corlys Velaryon</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Plot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Plot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Production\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Production</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Conception_and_development\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Conception and development</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Casting\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Casting</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Filming_locations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Filming locations</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Broadcast\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Broadcast</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Plot\">Plot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sea_Snake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Plot\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><i>The Sea Snake</i> takes place decades before the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, focusing on Corlys Velaryon and his nine voyages on the ship <i><a href=\"/index.php/Sea_Snake\" title=\"Sea Snake\">Sea Snake</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Production\">Production</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sea_Snake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Production\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Conception_and_development\">Conception and development</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sea_Snake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Conception and development\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Nine Voyages</i> and Bruno Heller's involvement were first reported on 18 March 2021.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> On 9 March 2022, <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> confirmed these rumors and revealed that the working title had been changed to <i>The Sea Snake</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Casting\">Casting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sea_Snake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Casting\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>TBA as <a href=\"/index.php/Corlys_Velaryon\" title=\"Corlys Velaryon\">Corlys Velaryon</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Filming_locations\">Filming locations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sea_Snake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Filming locations\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Broadcast\">Broadcast</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sea_Snake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Broadcast\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sea_Snake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sea_Snake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/game-of-thrones-flea-bottom-nine-voyages-ten-thousand-ships\">https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/game-of-thrones-flea-bottom-nine-voyages-ten-thousand-ships</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external free\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2022/03/09/random-updates-and-bits-o-news/\">https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2022/03/09/random-updates-and-bits-o-news/</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/